  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To determine whether higher as compared with lower maintenance doses of clopidogrel can
      adequately improve the degree of platelet inhibition in carriers of a reduced-function
      CYP2C19 allele.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
